# Curious that it requires something which might be obsolete.

   version stable 2.30.1 2.30.0 2.28.1 2.28.0
   require pessulus pygtk
  category utility/editor
 attribute gnome
 attribute broke
    source $GNOME_URL sources/sabayon/${VERSION:0:4}/sabayon-$VERSION.tar.bz2
      info home http://www.gnome.org/
      opts --with-distro=gentoo --enable-static=no
      desc 'editor for GConf default and mandatory keys
Sabayon provides a sane way to edit GConf defaults and mandatory keys:
the same way you edit your desktop.
Sabayon launches profiles in an Xnest window.
Any changes you make in the Xnest window are saved back
to the profile file, which can then be applied to user accounts.'
